namespace Pizza

features
	Pizza {abstract}	
		mandatory
			Topping	
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella
			Size {abstract}	
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough	
				alternative
					Neapolitan
					Sicilian

		optional
			CheesyCrust

constraints
	!Neapolitan | !Salami
	!Neapolitan | !Ham
	Salami | Mozzarella | Ham => Neapolitan